@startuml
title State Transition Diagram - Complaint Lifecycle (Admin Perspective)

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor white
  BorderColor black
  FontColor black
}
skinparam arrow {
  Color black
  FontColor black
}
skinparam linetype ortho

[*] --> Pending : Complaint Submitted (User)

Pending --> Assigned : Assign to Worker (Admin)
Assigned --> InProgress : Work Started (Worker)
InProgress --> Resolved : Upload Resolution (Worker)
Resolved --> UnderVerification : Review Proof (Admin)
UnderVerification --> Verified : Resolution Accepted (Admin)
UnderVerification --> ReworkRequired : Resolution Rejected (Admin)
ReworkRequired --> InProgress : Rework by Worker
Verified --> Closed : Complaint Closed (System/Admin)
Closed --> [*]

@enduml
